The detector quality or efficiency was evaluated from the relative alterations of the bandgap:187ε=100Eg-E0Eg\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
